### 3H. Wrap-Up Call Feature (Center FAB / Scheduled)

This is a **simulated incoming call screen** — not a SIM call.

**Trigger:** 5 minutes before a class ends (via WorkManager background task) OR manually via center FAB button.

**UI — Incoming Call Screen:**
- Full-screen dark overlay
- Large animated pulsing circle (electric blue glow)
- Text: `Lorenzo is calling...`
- Subtitle: `Class ending in 5 minutes — time to wrap up`
- School name + grade shown
- Three action buttons:
  - 🟢 **Answer** — opens voice debrief screen
  - 🔴 **Dismiss** — dismisses silently
  - 🟡 **Snooze** — reschedules for 2 minutes later (shown on call screen as a timer chip)
- Ringtone: soft chime (bundled asset, no SIM)
- Works even when phone is locked (uses `draw over other apps` permission + full-screen intent notification)

**After Answering — Voice Debrief Screen:**
- Waveform animation while recording (real-time amplitude visualization)
- Microphone button: tap to start/stop recording
- Status text: `Listening... speak naturally`
- After recording stops: spinner + `Processing your note...`
- Backend processes: Whisper (speech-to-text) → Groq LLM (extract tasks, names, deadlines, events) → structured JSON returned
- Structured output shown as:
  - List of extracted tasks (with auto-assigned priority)
  - Detected names (students/teachers) — shown as tags
  - Detected deadlines — shown with date
  - Free-form summary paragraph
- User can edit/delete any extracted item
- **Save** adds all to calendar/task list; **Discard** deletes

